#. <section class="sutta" id="an9.14"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.14:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.14:0.2"
msgid "2. Sīhanādavagga"
msgstr "2. The Lion’s Roar"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.14:0.3"
msgid "14. Samiddhisutta"
msgstr "14. With Samiddhi"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an9.14:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā samiddhi yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho "
"āyasmantaṃ samiddhiṃ āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Samiddhi went up to Venerable Sāriputta, bowed, and stood to "
"one side. Venerable Sāriputta said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an9.14:2.1"
msgid "“Kimārammaṇā, samiddhi, purisassa saṅkappavitakkā uppajjantī”ti?"
msgstr "“Samiddhi, based on what do thoughts arise in a person?”"

msgctxt "an9.14:2.2"
msgid "“Nāmarūpārammaṇā, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“Based on name and form, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an9.14:3.1"
msgid "“Te pana, samiddhi, kva nānattaṃ gacchantī”ti?"
msgstr "“Where do they become diversified?”"

msgctxt "an9.14:3.2"
msgid "“Dhātūsu, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“In the elements.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an9.14:4.1"
msgid "“Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃsamudayā”ti?"
msgstr "“What is their origin?”"

msgctxt "an9.14:4.2"
msgid "“Phassasamudayā, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“Contact is their origin.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an9.14:5.1"
msgid "“Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃsamosaraṇā”ti?"
msgstr "“What is their meeting place?”"

msgctxt "an9.14:5.2"
msgid "“Vedanāsamosaraṇā, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“Feeling is their meeting place.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an9.14:6.1"
msgid "“Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃpamukhā”ti?"
msgstr "“What is their chief?”"

msgctxt "an9.14:6.2"
msgid "“Samādhippamukhā, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“Immersion is their chief.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an9.14:7.1"
msgid "“Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃadhipateyyā”ti?"
msgstr "“What is their ruler?”"

msgctxt "an9.14:7.2"
msgid "“Satādhipateyyā, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“Mindfulness is their ruler.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an9.14:8.1"
msgid "“Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃuttarā”ti?"
msgstr "“What is their overseer?”"

msgctxt "an9.14:8.2"
msgid "“Paññuttarā, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“Wisdom is their overseer.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an9.14:9.1"
msgid "“Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃsārā”ti?"
msgstr "“What is their core?”"

msgctxt "an9.14:9.2"
msgid "“Vimuttisārā, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“Freedom is their core.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an9.14:10.1"
msgid "“Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃogadhā”ti?"
msgstr "“What is their culmination?”"

msgctxt "an9.14:10.2"
msgid "“Amatogadhā, bhante”ti."
msgstr "“They culminate in the deathless.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.386"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an9.14:11.1"
msgid ""
"“‘Kimārammaṇā, samiddhi, purisassa saṅkappavitakkā uppajjantī’ti, iti puṭṭho "
"samāno ‘nāmarūpārammaṇā, bhante’ti vadesi."
msgstr ""
"“Samiddhi, when you were asked what is the basis on which thoughts arise in "
"a person, you answered ‘name and form’."

msgctxt "an9.14:11.2"
msgid ""
"‘Te pana, samiddhi, kva nānattaṃ gacchantī’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno ‘dhātūsu, "
"bhante’ti vadesi."
msgstr "When you were asked …"

msgctxt "an9.14:11.3"
msgid ""
"‘Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃsamudayā’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno ‘phassasamudayā, "
"bhante’ti vadesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.14:11.4"
msgid ""
"‘Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃsamosaraṇā’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno ‘vedanāsamosaraṇā, "
"bhante’ti vadesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.14:11.5"
msgid ""
"‘Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃpamukhā’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno ‘samādhippamukhā, "
"bhante’ti vadesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.14:11.6"
msgid ""
"‘Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃadhipateyyā’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno ‘satādhipateyyā, "
"bhante’ti vadesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.14:11.7"
msgid ""
"‘Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃuttarā’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno ‘paññuttarā, bhante’ti "
"vadesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.14:11.8"
msgid ""
"‘Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃsārā’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno ‘vimuttisārā, bhante’ti "
"vadesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.14:11.9"
msgid ""
"‘Te pana, samiddhi, kiṃogadhā’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno ‘amatogadhā, bhante’ti "
"vadesi."
msgstr "what is their culmination, you answered ‘the deathless’."

msgctxt "an9.14:11.10"
msgid "Sādhu sādhu, samiddhi."
msgstr "Good, good, Samiddhi!"

#. VAR: puṭṭho → pañhaṃ (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an9.14:11.11"
msgid ""
"Sādhu kho tvaṃ, samiddhi, puṭṭho puṭṭho vissajjesi, tena ca mā maññī”ti."
msgstr ""
"It’s good that you answered each question. But don’t get conceited because "
"of that.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.14:11.12"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
